<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221888>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 48. Habitus. 41, 42, Paranoplischius modestus sp. nov. (dorsal, lateral); 43, 44, Paranoplischius nigellus sp. nov. (dorsal, lateral); 45 – 48, Paratractosomus sulciventris sp. nov. (dorsal, lateral, ventrolateral)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221886>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 33. Paratractosomus sulciventris sp. nov. 23, antenna; 24, frons and pronotum; 25, prothorax (lateral); 26, prosternal spine and mesosternal cavity; 27, meso- and metathorax (lateral); 28, sternite VIII; 29, sternite IX; 30, tergite VIII; 31, tergites IX – X; 32, 33, aedeagus (dorsal, ventral). Bars = 5 mm, except figs 23 – 27 = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221886/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221887>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34 – 40. Paratractosomus sulciventris sp. nov. 34, labrum; 35, labium; 36 – 39, mandible (dorsal, ventral); 40, maxilla. Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221887/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

